1. Aozora Bunko annotation specification snapshots (fair use / quotation)
================================================================================

HTML snapshots of the Aozora Bunko (青空文庫) annotation specification
are reproduced under docs/specs/aozora/ verbatim for offline technical
reference during aozora development. The material is (c) Aozora Bunko
volunteers and remains their property; aozora includes the snapshots
under a limited fair-use / quotation exception grounded in the fact that
the text is short, stable, and central to an interoperability effort.

See docs/specs/aozora/README.md for the full list of upstream URLs, the
snapshot date, and the rights-holder removal policy: if a rights-holder
requests removal, the files will be dropped and offline access will fall
back to fetching against the live site.


